## üìå Operatori de comparare

| Operator | Name                       | Example |
|----------|----------------------------|---------|
| ==       | Equal                      | x == y  |
| !=       | Not equal                  | x != y  |
| &gt;     | Greater than               | x > y   |
| &lt;     | Less than                  | x < y   |
| &gt;=    | Greater than or equal than | x >= y  |
| <=       | Less than or equal to      | x <= y  |

